modDescription:
This mod increases the crafting queue from 4 [slots](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-more-slots/) to 12\. Scrap everything!

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/KhaineGB/khaines-modlets-a19/-/archive/master/khaines-modlets-a19-master.zip?path=KHA19-12CraftQueue)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/19558-khaines-a19-modlets-bigger-backpacks-backpack-buttons-hp-bars-etc/).
